<td valign="middle" align="left">NURBS are not supported, Implicit Geometries are not supported .ExternalReferences are not supported.</td>
</tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left">Appearance</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left">PARTIAL</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left">the CityGML class TexCoordGen is not supported, ie one must specify the UV coordinates in the texture files.</td>
</tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left">Bridge</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left">YES</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left"/></tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left">Building</td>
