<td valign="middle" align="left">YES</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left"/></tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left">CityObjectGroup</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left">PARTIAL</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left">groups of City Objects are supported, but not groups of parts of objects (eg it is not possible to group some walls of a building together)</td>
</tr><tr><td valign="middle" align="left">Construction</td>
