<td valign="middle" align="left">(where only elevation points and break lines are stored) is not supported since it would require viewer/applications to have a constrained Delaunay triangulator, which is problematic (especially for web-based tools). Also, it is not possible to store areas over a terrain that would support different resolutions.</td>
