      <abstract format="text/plain" language="en" script="Latn">This document defines an integrated XML implementation of ISO 19115-1 and ISO 19115-2 by defining the following artefacts:
—     a set of XML schema required to validate metadata instance documents conforming to conceptual model elements defined in ISO 19115-1 and ISO 19115-2; and
